			<title>10 Tickets left!</title>
			<link>http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=204:10-tickets-left</link>
			<guid>http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=204:10-tickets-left</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p><img alt="logo_mail" src="http://www.european-games-award.com/images/stories/logo_mail.jpg" height="277" width="554" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Hurry up!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>The <strong>European Games Award 2012</strong> is in less then a week and here is your chance to grab one of the last <strong>10 tickets</strong> for the show!</p>
<p>be part of <strong>Europe's biggest people's choice award</strong> show in games and meet international game developers in person.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>People like <strong>Charles Cecil</strong> from Revolution Software, <strong>Karl Magnus</strong> from DICE, <strong>Victor Kislyi</strong> from Wargaming.net and many more will present more then 10 on-stage categories.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_wrapper&amp;view=wrapper&amp;Itemid=30"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><br /></span></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_wrapper&amp;view=wrapper&amp;Itemid=30"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Okay, I want my ticket now!</span></a></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
