			<title>Intermediate Results Disabled</title>
			<link>http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=203:intermediate-results-disabled</link>
			<guid>http://www.european-games-award.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=203:intermediate-results-disabled</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p> </p>
<p><img src="http://www.european-games-award.com/images/stories/header_small_update.jpg" alt="header_small_update" height="135" width="580" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Seven days to go on the European Games Award 2012!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>As planned we disabled the intermediate results to keep the tension high for this year's <strong>European Games Award</strong>.</p>
<p>We will have ten on-stage categories with various laudators like <strong>Charles Cecil</strong> from Revolution Software, <strong>Karl Magnus</strong> from DICE, <strong>Victor Kislyi</strong> from Wargaming.net and many many more!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Stay tuned for <strong>Europe's biggest people's choice award</strong> show in games!</p>]]></description>
